<collectingCountry id="F345B1D7D649DC0221B4FEDBB6016660" box="[956,1029,752,778]" name="Egypt" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Egypt</collectingCountry>
, but we never confirmed this citation; we also know records from 
<collectingCountry id="F345B1D7D649DC022012FF33B06F6658" box="[538,619,792,818]" name="Jordan" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Jordan</collectingCountry>
, which need confirmation.
</paragraph>
